"Returns an array of dimensions (similar to <command>dim()</command> in R)."
msgstr ""
"Returnerar ett fält med dimensioner (liknar <command>dim()</command> i R)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3312
#, no-c-format
msgid "classes()"
msgstr "classes()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3312
#, no-c-format
